title: Rittal CMC-III Units: Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/rittal
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors sensors which provide only a status and no
 further information like e.g. the maintenance interval or the
 battery change of Rittal CMC-III units. The state returned by
 the Rittal device is converted to the state of the check plugin
 as follows:
 If the Rittal device returns {OK}, the check is {OK}. Otherwise
 the check is {CRIT}.

item:
 The unit name and the name of the sensor

discovery:
 One service is created for each sensor.
